===Etymology 1===
According to {{zh-ref|Schuessler (2007)}}, either:
* related to {{cog|lus|hlo||a weed, drug, medicine}}, or
* cognate to {{och-l|療|to treat, to cure}}, thus beloning to the same word family as {{och-l|瀹}}, {{och-l|爍}}.

